the political survey season is coming 
mercifully to an end for the 6438 democratic and republican 
convention delegates who have had to endure 1001 questions from 
the news media and so too for the rest of us whove suffered the 
cumulative results 
is there a collective national amen 
the delegates chosen by their fellow party members to pick 
