wont be released for several weeks but that union claims that 
eastern is facing a 20 percent to 25 percent reduction in flight 
hours is probably pretty factual 
surely the fall schedule hasnt been put to bed yet and 
itll probably change 50 times before it is put to bed powell 
said as it now stands we may see a reduction but we have no 
intentions of withdrawing from palm beach 
eastern is a subsidiary of houstonbased texas air corp the 
nations largest airline company 
